data.description: Spacious 4 bedroom, 2 bath, 2500 SF home, renovated in 2020 qualifies for RD, FHA, VA or conventional. 2020 renovations included, new roof, electrical update, HVAC, appliances, water heater, lighting, hard wood floors refinished and paint. The kitchen features ship-lap accent wall. The home has high ceilings and decorative crown throughout and the wood floors are absolutely gorgeous! The primary bedroom has an ensuite bath with claw foot tub! Picturesque windows and attention to detail throughout. Upstairs is a bonus room that would make great playroom, office, man cave or bedroom.  Spacious backyard with large workshop! Schedule your appointment today.
